| Migrations | `golang-migrate/migrate/v4` | SQL files in `db/migrations/` |
| Validation | `go-playground/validator/v10` | Struct-tag driven |
| Tests | `stretchr/testify` + `testcontainers-go` | Real Postgres in containers |
| Feature flags | OpenFeature Go SDK (via `pkg/featureflag`) | Any OpenFeature provider |

